{"id": "ChIJFzGif5THwoARIrium1HFeuY", "rating": 4.3, "userRatingCount": 64, "displayName": {"text": "Cafe Knotted Arts District", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJFzGif5THwoARIrium1HFeuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psUmF6RnFNVWN0YW5WTlJXVlVVMFEzUVdWNVkxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Cafe Knotted in the Arts District was absolutely worth the visit. We tried the fresh strawberry milk cream, butter rice cake, Dubai chocolate, and honey garlic bun, and every single item was delicious. The strawberry milk cream was creamy yet surprisingly light and fresh, while the butter rice cake had the perfect chewy texture without being overly sweet. Everything felt well balanced and thoughtfully made. Can’t wait to come back and try more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cafe Knotted in the Arts District was absolutely worth the visit. We tried the fresh strawberry milk cream, butter rice cake, Dubai chocolate, and honey garlic bun, and every single item was delicious. The strawberry milk cream was creamy yet surprisingly light and fresh, while the butter rice cake had the perfect chewy texture without being overly sweet. Everything felt well balanced and thoughtfully made. Can’t wait to come back and try more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "PeterY129", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108127635440357326876/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEV35kve99CYRRn9Vh6bhOGhMFtlAFNNX0ypwhSefySNSlzfU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T22:34:38.240473408Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psUmF6RnFNVWN0YW5WTlJXVlVVMFEzUVdWNVkxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psUmF6RnFNVWN0YW5WTlJXVlVVMFEzUVdWNVkxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7947fa23117:0xe67ac5519baeb822"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzGif5THwoARIrium1HFeuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pnelQyWjFNMmhXZDJad2NXaGxMV290ZW5ad1ZIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Having been to Santa Monica outlet couple times and aware that they recent expanded into Arts District, with much cuter space. Handful of parking space available around, which was certainly a PLUS PLUS knowing how tough this area was.\n\nThey still carried their signature doughnuts and cookies, but further increasing the options with basque cheesecake and butter tteok, yep that hype thing you might have seen thousand times on your screen.\n\nI was tad in a rush so I could just stop by for a drink. Also kind of a bummer that it's relatively slow to get the drink ready despite it's not like busy busy. I got their crowd's favorite Banana Cream Latte, coming with banana milk base, my choice of milk (picking almond), espresso shot, and banana cream top. Overall the coffee was okay to me, but the banana flavor was bit subtle for my liking. Might make a come back for their butter tteok some time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Having been to Santa Monica outlet couple times and aware that they recent expanded into Arts District, with much cuter space. Handful of parking space available around, which was certainly a PLUS PLUS knowing how tough this area was.\n\nThey still carried their signature doughnuts and cookies, but further increasing the options with basque cheesecake and butter tteok, yep that hype thing you might have seen thousand times on your screen.\n\nI was tad in a rush so I could just stop by for a drink. Also kind of a bummer that it's relatively slow to get the drink ready despite it's not like busy busy. I got their crowd's favorite Banana Cream Latte, coming with banana milk base, my choice of milk (picking almond), espresso shot, and banana cream top. Overall the coffee was okay to me, but the banana flavor was bit subtle for my liking. Might make a come back for their butter tteok some time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "JG", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111257583310582062343/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8UqbsVHg2VxS0LgD7ECyFYYeCZ3BA4Dt0ktxf3VxgqHOQs4o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-23T06:46:42.280609302Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pnelQyWjFNMmhXZDJad2NXaGxMV290ZW5ad1ZIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pnelQyWjFNMmhXZDJad2NXaGxMV290ZW5ad1ZIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7947fa23117:0xe67ac5519baeb822"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzGif5THwoARIrium1HFeuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWNU0xTjRTRzVtVldGNVJUVkpTMlZaTldSMVZHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The place was so comforting, music was on point. The donut was so yummy, not too sweet not bland too. I also tried the matcha, it’s so good. Thank you to Megan for providing amazing service. I love Megan 💕💕", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The place was so comforting, music was on point. The donut was so yummy, not too sweet not bland too. I also tried the matcha, it’s so good. Thank you to Megan for providing amazing service. I love Megan 💕💕", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Vivian02", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114165856729918851444/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ-iUYSxS2B7U7e19oNXG4WzeyMUTfEmKIQ7ygUyDqeUycyw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-27T03:06:08.972089149Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWNU0xTjRTRzVtVldGNVJUVkpTMlZaTldSMVZHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWNU0xTjRTRzVtVldGNVJUVkpTMlZaTldSMVZHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7947fa23117:0xe67ac5519baeb822"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzGif5THwoARIrium1HFeuY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKd1gwUTBlazF4Wm1SMmRHMHdWWFU0ZUdWSmMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This was undoubtedly a very HAPPY MOMENT. I love doughnuts, I went specifically for the Corn flavored pastry. The flavor of the bread, not to sweet and the filling were so pure that it didn't feel like a Donut. I also got the Matcha Cheesecake, great unsweetened and not over powering matcha flavor, loved it so much. I can not t imagine what the other pastries taste like, \"Knotted\" is definitely a well-deserved go to pastry shop.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This was undoubtedly a very HAPPY MOMENT. I love doughnuts, I went specifically for the Corn flavored pastry. The flavor of the bread, not to sweet and the filling were so pure that it didn't feel like a Donut. I also got the Matcha Cheesecake, great unsweetened and not over powering matcha flavor, loved it so much. I can not t imagine what the other pastries taste like, \"Knotted\" is definitely a well-deserved go to pastry shop.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brenda Cantellano", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103345846425211035674/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLO9lspPsghMahZ2DWtPCDUEV2a0b7vyBQAutGKT93_Fkkl8A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T19:36:12.258911049Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKd1gwUTBlazF4Wm1SMmRHMHdWWFU0ZUdWSmMwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKd1gwUTBlazF4Wm1SMmRHMHdWWFU0ZUdWSmMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7947fa23117:0xe67ac5519baeb822"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFzGif5THwoARIrium1HFeuY/reviews/Ci9DQ